            "title": "The crew",
            "color_title": "",
            "size_text": "h2",
            "text": "",
            "answer_content": "<p>One thing in common: a true dedication to their passion. It all started with a bunch of friends hanging out by the river. It turned into a community. Fly fishers from around the world, connected by their passion for great fly fishing vibes, compose the Astro.</p>",
